Date: Mon, 14 May 2001 02:15:00 -0700 (PDT)
From: jeffery.fawcett@enron.com
To: glen.hass@enron.com, mbaldwin@igservice.com, jeff.dasovich@enron.com
Subject: I9907003 Ruling re Notice of a Full Panel Hearing
Body: 
Cc: kimberly.watson@enron.com, steven.harris@enron.com
Bcc: kimberly.watson@enron.com, steven.harris@enron.com
Team,
Let's shoot for Tuesday, May 15, at 2:00 p.m. CDT, 12: 00 noon, PDT.  Mark, 
we'll call you.  Jeff, I don't know if you're available, but if you've got a 
spare minute, it'd probably be a good idea for us to rally by phone before 
the Hearing.  Glen, I'll call you also.
Kim, Steve, if you guys want to sit-in, we'll make the call from one of the 
offices. 

 -----Original Message-----
From:  mbaldwin@igservice.com@ENRON 
[mailto:IMCEANOTES-mbaldwin+40igservice+2Ecom+40ENRON@ENRON.com] 
Sent: Friday, May 11, 2001 6:27 PM
To: Fawcett, Jeffery
Subject: RE: I9907003 Ruling re Notice of a Full Panel Hearing
Jeff, I am available Tuesday 12 noon to 1:30 pm or first thing Wednesday
morning or almost all afternoon Wednesday. Monday , I am traveling. Mark,
IGS    Have a great weekend.
> -----Original Message-----
> From: Fawcett, Jeffery [mailto:Jeffery.Fawcett@ENRON.com]
